{"tid":191064,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好怕同屋企人去旅行","createTime":"2017-04-07T14:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T11:07:49.000Z","uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88e0731518f9a5bc76e0623ba5750d87fe51fd5e","tid":191064,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"大家後生把握機會就同屋企人去下旅行啦<br />\n你而家唔去<br />\n等佢地老左你想同佢地去都好難架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間追唔番的,你而家唔去,將來你會發現愈來愈難同佢地去其他國家<br />\n同屋企人去未必夠同朋友去開心<br />\n但你唔去第時先後悔就太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n申利:屋企人好好,單純9up下"},{"pid":"c7ff9ceda4ba244a5bb3a00fbc64b0500b54d7f5","tid":191064,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"我好想同屋企人去旅行<br />\n22歲人一次都無同屋企人去過旅行<br />\n細個果陣就話老豆搵得唔多<br />\n又要養我同呀哥<br />\n今年我都grad <br />\n老豆又搵得多過以前<br />\n但係呀媽就話唔想舟車勞頓<br />\n唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以拉到老母肯去旅行"},{"pid":"6dceae10e4b811c7ce9afa4e8cccf82d669f3039","tid":191064,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好想同屋企人去旅行<br />\n22歲人一次都無同屋企人去過旅行<br />\n細個果陣就話老豆搵得唔多<br />\n又要養我同呀哥<br />\n今年我都grad <br />\n老豆又搵得多過以前<br />\n但係呀媽就話唔想舟車勞頓<br />\n唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以拉到老母肯去旅行</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df20b754836083288885e61fb697fb462a8676d","tid":191064,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好想同屋企人去旅行<br />\n22歲人一次都無同屋企人去過旅行<br />\n細個果陣就話老豆搵得唔多<br />\n又要養我同呀哥<br />\n今年我都grad <br />\n老豆又搵得多過以前<br />\n但係呀媽就話唔想舟車勞頓<br />\n唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以拉到老母肯去旅行</blockquote><br />\n我同你相反係老豆唔願去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我機票酒店都預埋佢果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔想我蝕錢所以最後都一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔怕都可以試吓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋試吓畀plans老母睇同老母講行程唔會咁chur周圍去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0136576f6a57c33b7ee136aa97473c4272db6248","tid":191064,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好想同屋企人去旅行<br />\n22歲人一次都無同屋企人去過旅行<br />\n細個果陣就話老豆搵得唔多<br />\n又要養我同呀哥<br />\n今年我都grad <br />\n老豆又搵得多過以前<br />\n但係呀媽就話唔想舟車勞頓<br />\n唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以拉到老母肯去旅行</blockquote><br />\n我老母都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆就唔鐘意日韓<br />\n屋企又多人 講左十年都未去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8409ad59a60ab89789c1f7151e1d85a3c1193ef","tid":191064,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:33:17.000Z","msg":"除左大陸團未試過成家一齊去旅行<br />\n好想同佢地去但佢地意欲唔太大<br />\n同埋又要湊我隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a8a84485f2e81761c3b530f3d551eda3287aaa","tid":191064,"uid":87724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過同全家一齊去旅行，又試過單獨同阿媽去旅行，兩次都自由行。<br />\n結論係：一係跟團，否則以後唔會再去。"},{"pid":"8e97c9c216ec5def9a75947888c774950274a0da","tid":191064,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過同全家一齊去旅行，又試過單獨同阿媽去旅行，兩次都自由行。<br />\n結論係：一係跟團，否則以後唔會再去。</blockquote><br />\n同屋企人去旅行係去hea<br />\n唔係去趕景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169beb9fa2150a983e3a784a8da5768a5afbc2ea","tid":191064,"uid":45110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"一定要跟團 有人安排好哂俾佢地 唔駛自己搵車搭 點到點咁接送佢地先得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114bdcc0ceea71e32888639b4b35f57cfb810f78","tid":191064,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"會好怕 但都會好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n怕係因為始終後生有後生想玩嘅玩法 適用唔到係父母到，佢地又好易嫌三嫌四<br />\n想去係因為想創造多啲一家人一齊嘅回憶。香港地咁忙 郊遊都唔得閒去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d774e06cd93fe8aade8ec2642ee7ef2272f050a","tid":191064,"uid":75751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"我亞媽囉！同我地自己一家人去佢就唔去，但係同佢D兄弟姐妹即係我舅父亞姨佢就會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac47799ec5a1c0e2450e1754a6172ea5605b9b70","tid":191064,"uid":31725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"黎緊同屋企人去冰島同英國自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好緊張 第一次同家姐帶屋企人去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f5dad196ec6c8ac2390e065c3a0d1882bf7856","tid":191064,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"1～2年一次，夾屋企人要就學校假期，都幾煩。<br />\n<br />\n早計劃，又驚有人到時唔得，遲計劃啲機票又貴！"}]}